    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior upholstery shows some fading and minor wear in high-traffic areas. Mechanically, it runs well, but it will likely need routine maintenance soon, such as new brake pads or a tune-up. It is a solid, functional car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
