    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a well-loved car that has seen the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of any rips or significant wear, while the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the responsive touchscreen interface to the heated seats and panoramic sunroof, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection just completed. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts with crisp precision, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. With a clean title and a full set of service records included, this vehicle is ready for its next chapter with an owner who appreciates a car that has been cared for properly.",
